580
00:41:38,840 --> 00:41:43,060
If it were someone else, they would probably be at their wits' end.

581
00:41:46,860 --> 00:41:50,360
Then I hope you can solve the case soon.

582
00:41:53,120 --> 00:41:55,400
There are many people...

